# Demo Seed Data

- All important screens must have realistic fake data.
- No real private information.
- Demo data must connect across modules.
- Customer demo must not show empty screens.
- Include demo states for pending, approved, rejected, blocked, reported, and review-needed flows where relevant.
- Keep seed data deterministic and resettable.

